Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:04.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,162)}时光胶囊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.20,0:01:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢各位莅临今天的时光胶囊典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for attending today's time capsule ceremony
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常有必要让未来一代了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's important that future generations know
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让裤头村出众的特点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what made Bikini Bottom special
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及裤头村居民与其任意的个人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,its citizens and their random personal belongings
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.59,0:01:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  请欢迎珊迪奇克斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, please welcome Miss Sandy Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.64,0:01:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢市长小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Miss Mayor
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我设计了这个金属容器
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.93,0:01:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I designed this metallic vessel
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以完美保存里面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:25.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to perfectly preserve anything inside
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过有一个特定的时限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a very specific amount of time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时限多少呢  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:30.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much time, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  大约两千年左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, like, 2,000-ish years
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,典礼开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the ceremony begin
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想留一条快乐好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to leave a happy message
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为明天的居民们听
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the good people of tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好高档的垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a fancy trash can
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿我竖笛干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with my clarinet?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让它变成未来的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making it the future's problem
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让开  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of my way, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来的客人肯定会出高价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Customers of the future will pay top dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买个陈年原版蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a vintage original Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能现在直接收钱吗  还是要再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I charge for this now or do I have to wait?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本次重要典礼到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that concludes this momentous occasion
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢大家来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much for--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急着走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fools
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有蟹黄堡在手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With this patty in my grasp
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于能统治世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can finally take over the world
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe later
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两千年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,2,000 years
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很久以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Much later
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得把你们都消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to destroy you all
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚说到  感谢大家莅临
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As I was saying, thanks for coming, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,市政厅送免费匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free pizza at city hall
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.03,0:03:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,匹萨  匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pizza, pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次又惹上什么麻烦了  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you gotten yourself into this time, Sheldon?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  快给我开罐器什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, get me a can opener or something, quick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来只能等它自己打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, guess we have to wait until it opens up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来日再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两千年左右之后
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靠每顿一个蟹黄堡分子维持生命体征
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,after surviving on this patty one molecule at a time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算破解秘密配方了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've finally cracked the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的恐怖统治终于能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now my reign of terror can be--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这垃圾堆看着没那么垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This dump looks less dumpy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来一定很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future must be pretty great
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.04,0:04:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟一切都是铬做的  还挺滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if everything's made of chrome, and slidey
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1366,762)}铬之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铬之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Chrome Bucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the door?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进不去实验室还怎么统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take over the world if I can't even get into my lab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  放我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, let me in
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿  欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon, welcome home
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好像整容了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you've had some work done
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我整的东西多着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's not the only work I've been doing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.83,0:04:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你完成了某种致命毁灭机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you completed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some kind of deadly destructive robot?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Negative
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在做艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have been working on my art pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实还挺成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm quite successful, in fact
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  这东西很配客厅沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey, this would match the couch in the living room
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们买了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁稀罕什么艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who cares about art?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来帮我统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to help me take over the world
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大门怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what happened to the front door?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.03,0:05:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不明白  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天下已经大变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whole world is different now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1550,326)}章鱼哥博物馆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是章鱼哥的老房子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Squidward's old house
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Museum of Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁会去参观纪念那废物的博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who would ever go to a museum dedicated to that loser?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来参观的有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lots of people
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥以前的竖笛录音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's old clarinet recordings
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是公认的古典乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are considered classical music now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以前大伙完全不把它当音乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They weren't considered music at all before
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.81,0:05:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜他逝世后  作品才得到大众欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sadly, no one started listening to them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until the day after he was gone
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的石头现在长这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is what Patrick's rock looks like now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那笨蛋向来是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That moron was always an idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的破汽水杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And his stupid soda cup
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我两千年都黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,left me sticky for 2,000 years
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he were here right now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就给他松弛的下巴来一记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd sock him right in his slack jaw
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.30,0:06:07.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位是派一千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:07.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is the P-1000
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要吃铬金属点心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a chrome snack
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算他变机器人了也是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even as a robot he's an idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道不像是铬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This doesn't taste like chrome
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要继续睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:24.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to bed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let me guess--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你接下来要给我看海绵宝宝怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,next, you're going to show me what happened to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来没这打算  但你要看就看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't, but if you insist
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷哥酷姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, cats
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it hanging?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢顺道过来  懂不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for stopping by, ya dig?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.38,0:06:54.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里居然会有东西真的改善了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:54.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe something here has actually improved
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且那东西就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that something was you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是他的全息门卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's his holographic doorman
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是真正的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:05.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the real SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少是他的残余物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or at least what's left of him
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He likes you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让它住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it stop
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.49,0:07:20.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那笑声的回声已经困扰我两千年了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:20.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was haunted by the echoes of that laugh for 2,000 years
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, I get it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future is awful
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我现在知道秘密配方了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I know the secret formula now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能统治这个垃圾时间线了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can take over this horrible timeline
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About that
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,似乎还有一点东西得让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think there's something else you should see
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,344)}铬堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铬堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Kromey Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因生锈永久停业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Permanently closed due to rust"
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great news
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不见得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王营不营业都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if the Krusty Krab is open or not
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来居民全都知道秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the future, everyone knows the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They what?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had it with the future
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想回到我恨的那些臭鱼烂虾身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to go back to all the people I hate
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不早说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认识可能会帮得上忙的某位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know someone who might be able to help
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个怪松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The screwy squirrel?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正那松鼠也没被困在管子里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The squirrel didn't get trapped in a tube
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整整两千年  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for 2,000 years, did she?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有点道理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touché, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太诡异了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is weird
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪家样子完全没变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's place looks exactly the same
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  但是注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indeed, but be warned
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.26,0:09:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪可能与你记忆中的样子不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy may not be exactly how you remember her
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆  敢敲我树屋的门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares to knock upon my dome?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.20,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.20,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.75,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪·奇克斯听候差遣  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.75,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy Cheeks at your service, Mr. Plankton.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么变年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how did you get younger?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.13,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在穿越时空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.13,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've just been jumping through the ages
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.25,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从珊瑚营地夏令营结束后就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.25,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,since summer ended at Kamp Koral.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以是在探索时空是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just exploring space and time, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你带我回到现代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please take me back to the present, please
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我讨厌未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate the future
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.14,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用求我  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.14,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,No need to beg, Mr. Plankton.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.94,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.94,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.36,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,时光机的燃料已经充满了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.36,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,The time hopper's all gassed up.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时光机在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, where is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.49,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你站的地方就是时光机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.49,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're standing in it, partner.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.49,0:09:59.03,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座树屋就是我的反向时光胶囊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:59.03,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here tree dome is my reverse time capsule.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还等什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away we go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两千年前见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you 2,000 years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.76,0:10:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以出来了  痞老板二点零
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can come out now, Plankton 2.0
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为他要赖在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought he'd never leave
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往我身上涂点铬吧  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now lay some chrome on me, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,792)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到我会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd say this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太想念这个烂地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I missed this horrible place
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你帮忙什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And thank you for your help or whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be gone now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.00,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是忘了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.00,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块钱找得开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you break a single?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.42,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用给小费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.42,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need a tip
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.30,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,但得让你忘掉秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.30,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I will need you to forget that secret formula.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动  我要启动我的记忆消除装置了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold still while I activate my memory-erasing device.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your what?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.55,一般-Chi,,0,0,0,,夏令营再见  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.55,一般-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you back at camp, Mr. Plankton.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did I get here?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来的客人肯定会出高价
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Customers of the future will pay top dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买个陈年原版蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:23.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a vintage original Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急着走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fools
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁有似曾相识的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is anyone else having déjà vu?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.63,0:11:42.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两千年左右再见  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:42.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you in 2,000-ish years, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两千年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,2,000 years
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.56,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:57.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,598)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:05.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,880)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is served
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今早声音不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure sound different this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是娜琳的海骡子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Narlene's sea mule
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是来看我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1270,722)}播放我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,播放我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Play me"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会诺比语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I speak Nobbese
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就帮你翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll translate for you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳和诺比邀请你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene and Nobby invite you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且绝对没请章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and definitely not Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来参加家族年度黄蜂水母酱大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to our family's Annual Bumble Jelly Harvest
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地点在裤头呼喊谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Holler
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这则录音自爆倒计时  三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This recording will self-destruct in three
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.22,0:13:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ze--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖一点  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be a good boy, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be back later
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.08,0:13:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们上路要前往裤头呼喊谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're on our way to Bikini Holler
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.21,0:13:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在身后的道路缩得越来越小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The road behind us is getting smaller
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绿草青青
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The grass is green
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树木变得高高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the trees are taller
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送一块钱  我就不会再唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll stop yodeling for just a dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛要停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why in tarnation are we stopping?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点啊  骡子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, mule
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:55.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get moving
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下面的小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out below
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In the flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊  娜琳跟诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Narlene and Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的骡子好像完全不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seems your mule just plum stopped moving
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不然打开它  看看引擎怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't I open her up and check the engine?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长脑袋是干什么用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you even have a head, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样雨水不会流进脖子上的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It keeps the rain out of my neck hole
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之所以骡子不愿意走这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The mule refuses to walk through these parts
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为这段路会经过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause this here road goes right through--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,740)}浮游生物领地
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮游生物领地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton Territory?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独角鲸禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Narwhals keep out"?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回去  独角鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go home, Narwhals
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是浮游生物的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This here is Plankton land
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.46,0:15:02.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们休想伸着花哨长牙来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:02.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't want your fancy ivory tusks around here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's skedaddle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们为什么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are they doing this?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮游生物和独角鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Planktons and the Narwhals
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是好几代的世仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have been feuding for generations
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们宣称黄蜂水母田是他们自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They claim the bumble jelly fields are theirs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那明明是我们的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while we know they're ours
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么不共享水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you share the fields?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那有什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, where's the fun in that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.87,0:15:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了  黄蜂水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we be, bumble jelly fields
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的兄弟在那用角戳树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My brothers there peck the trees
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄蜂水母就在树里储存水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where the bumble jellies store their jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的姐妹在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My sisters over there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.01,0:15:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,则喜欢从蜂巢现挤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like to squeeze it fresh right out of the hive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长辈则更愿意吹小夜曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The old folks prefer to serenade
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让水母直接出水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the jelly out of the bumbles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见见我们爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,meet our ma and pa
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个粉红城市佬是跟你们一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:14.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, man, is that pink city slicker with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He sure is brave
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brave?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,之所以黄蜂水母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only reason the bumble jellies
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿意让我们采集水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let us collect their jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只因为我们同意被它们蜇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is because we allow 'em to sting us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们得被它们蜇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You let them sting you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn tootin'
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I consent
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太值得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's worth it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, there, son
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不要乱动  才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta hold still to complete the, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,社会契约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,social contract
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题不大  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that wasn't so bad now, was it?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.46,0:17:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄蜂水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bumble jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.13,0:17:18.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布  今年黄蜂水母酱大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I declare that this here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:18.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a bountiful bumper crop of beautiful bumble jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收成时间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harvest time is over
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.94,0:17:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄蜂水母节开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the bumble jelly festival commence
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Festival
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母坐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jelly flop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮廓不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good contour
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结构强劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strong structure
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,风格很大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A very bold mold
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们怎么有个穿大衣的表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is your cousin in the long trench coat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在打翻那个装水母酱的桶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tipping over that jelly barrel?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是表亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't no cousin
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他们尝尝厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let 'em have it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世仇来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got ourselves a feud
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lordy Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我中土豆弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been spud smacked
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备开火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire in the hole
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们浮游生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Them Planktons
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算能拿海底所有土豆扔我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can throw all the potatoes in the ocean at us
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是有一样特别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got us something special
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我们取得决定性胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that'll give us a decisive victory
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要更多土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need more taters
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家找掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone take cover
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没鞋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm out of shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经全都扔过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We plum tossed 'em all
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't rightly know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着像是鞋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要求休战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'd like a truce
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独角鲸和浮游生物没有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't no reason Narwhals and Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能共享水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can't share the fields
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况我们已经没弹药了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, we ran out of ammo
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪你们家爱吃土豆的城市佬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thanks to your tater-eating city slicker
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice work, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽职尽责是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was an honor to serve
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休战是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A truce, eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正我们也没鞋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, seeing as how we're all out of shoes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们想要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want 'em back?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, heck
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们留着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can keep 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.43,0:21:35.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此外我们也没觉得鞋子有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:35.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, we ain't found much use for 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:39.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happens now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.98,0:21:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一年一度仇后派对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The annual post-feud party
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一年一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Annual?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是说每年都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you do this every year?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure do
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's fun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们玩得不痛快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, didn't y'all have fun?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们并没有玩得痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did not have fun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The best day ever
